Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:11.36,UR,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.75\fad(1250,1250)\pos(1165,665)}Dvadsať tvárí
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hashiba, choď o krok doľava.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:17.46,Main,,0,0,0,,D-Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Na sekundu som sa vystrašil. Vďaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Nedotkol som sa ťa! Určite som sa ťa nedotkol!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,S-Si hotový?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Uf!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Akechi, už som ich opravil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Chlapče.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Áno?
